<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٢١٧ - عَنْ هِشَامٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ سِيرِينَ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" تُكَفَّنُ الْمَرْأَةُ فِي خَمْسَةِ أَثْوَابٍ: دِرْعٌ، وَخِمَارٌ، وَخِرْقَةٌ، وَلُفَافَتَيْنِ "</span>،<span class="c5"> قُلْنَا لِعَبْدِ الرَّزَّاقِ:</span> وَكَيْفَ يُصْنَعُ بِالْخِرْقَةِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> تُجْعَلُ كَهَيْئَةِ الْإِزَارِ مِنْ فَوْقِ الدِّرْعِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>